'''Armando Obispo''' (born 5 March 1999) is a professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[centre-back]] for [[PSV Eindhoven]].<ref name="soccerway">{{cite web|url=https://www.vitesse.nl/nl/nieuws/detail/7923/armando-obispo-eerste-aanwinst|title=ARMANDO OBISPO EERSTE AANWINST|website=www.vitesse.nl|accessdate=20 June 2019}}</ref> Born in the Netherlands, he plays for the [[Curaçao national football team|Curaçao national team]].

==Club career==
Obispo made his professional debut as [[Jong PSV]] player in the second division on 8 August 2016 against [[FC Den Bosch]].<ref name="soccerway2">{{cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2016/08/08/netherlands/eerste-divisie/jong-psv/fc-den-bosch/2240574/|title=Jong PSV vs. FC Den Bosch - 8 August 2016 - Soccerway|website=soccerway.com|accessdate=13 October 2016}}</ref>

== International career ==
On 26 September 2025, Obispo was handed his first call-up to the [[Curaçao national football team|Curaçao national team]] by manager [[Dick Advocaat]].<ref>{{Cite web |date=2025-09-26 |title=Obispo en Hansen maken interlandswitch en staan voor debuut |url=https://www.voetbalprimeur.nl/nieuws/1696101/obispo-en-hansen-voor-het-eerst-bij-cura-ao.html |access-date=2025-09-26 |website=VoetbalPrimeur.nl |language=nl-NL}}</ref> Five days later, his request to switch international allegiance to Curaçao was approved by [[FIFA]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://knowledge.fifa.com/change-of-association-platform|title=FIFA Change of Association Platform|publisher=[[FIFA]]|website=knowledge.fifa.com|access-date=1 October 2025}}</ref> In May 2026, he was named in Curaçao's squad for the [[2026 FIFA World Cup]], the country's first-ever appearance at the tournament.<ref>{{cite web|title=Smallest nation Curacao name debut World Cup squad|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/articles/c70798249j0o|date=18 May 2026|access-date=18 May 2026}}</ref>

==Personal life==
Obispo was born in the Netherlands and is of Curaçaoan descent.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://curacaonieuws.nu/curacaos-tintje-aan-landstitel-psv/|title=Curaçaos tintje aan landstitel PSV - Curacao Nieuws|date=16 April 2018|publisher=|access-date=26 August 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180826214624/https://curacaonieuws.nu/curacaos-tintje-aan-landstitel-psv/|archive-date=26 August 2018|url-status=dead}}</ref>

